    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, combine the <strong>softened</strong> <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut</strong> with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and gradually stir in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong>, mixing well to form a smooth paste – this is your <strong>creamed coconut mixture</strong></p>",
