    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut mixture</strong> to the pan (this will cause the liquid to thicken as it returns to the boil)</p><p>Break up the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>basa </strong>with a wooden spoon<strong> </strong>as you go</p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed – this is your <strong>smoky basa & coconut chowder</strong></p>",
